615
00:37:27,027 --> 00:37:28,945
Un exemplaire unique.

616
00:37:29,154 --> 00:37:30,279
- Vraiment ?
- Oui.

617
00:37:30,447 --> 00:37:31,322
Bonjour.

618
00:37:35,495 --> 00:37:37,203
- Attendez !
- Subtile.

619
00:37:38,873 --> 00:37:40,499
