760
00:44:32,128 --> 00:44:33,128
Deux airs chauds.

761
00:44:33,672 --> 00:44:34,922
Mais j'aime ça.

762
00:44:36,215 --> 00:44:38,551
J'ai pas l'air trop bizarre, j'espère ?

763
00:44:40,304 --> 00:44:41,262
Trop ?

764
00:44:41,555 --> 00:44:42,721
Trop.

765
00:44:43,515 --> 00:44:44,973
Passe-moi la brosse.

766
00:44:47,019 --> 00:44:48,644
Le voilà.

